Kumuñja — Mt. king of hills, to the east of Aruṇoda;1 
eight cities of the Dānavas located in.2 1) Vā. 36. 18; 37. 1.
 2) Ib. 39. 28-9.


कुमुथि
Kumuthi — a ṛtvik at Brahmā's sacrifice. 
Vā. 106. 34.

