Kumbha (III) — helped Soma in the Tārakāmaya war. 
Vi. IV. 6. 14.

कुम्भ
Kumbha (IV) — a palace in the shape of a pot, with 
9 bhūmikas and a toraṇa of 16 hastas. 
M. 269. 37-49.

कुम्भ
Kumbha (V) — fit for śrāddha. 
Vā. 77. 47.

