nected with the marriage of Rukminī and Kṛṣṇa.2 He praised 
Kṛṣṇa's heroism and welcomed him.3 Took part in the 
Rājasūya of Yudhiṣṭhira.4 He went to Syamantapañcaka for 
solar eclipse;5 migration of Yadus to.6 1) Bhā. I. 10. 34. X. [50 (V) 2]; II. 7. 35. Br. II. 18. 50; III. 
59. 3 and 46.
