Svāyambhuva; Yajña also Yāma;4 constitutes Dharma and 
mantra; the Yajva goes to heaven;5 a soma yajus of paśu, 
dravya, havis, Ṛtviks, Dakṣiṇa.6 1) Bhā. I. 3. 12; III. 19. 13; IV. 1. 4-5; VI. 8. 15; VIII. 1. 6.
