Śrutaṃjaya (II) — a Bṛhadratha; ruled for 24 years. 
Br. III. 74. 114.

श्रुतंजय
Śrutaṃjaya (III) — ruled for 40 years. 
M. 271. 23; Vā. 99. 300.

