Śvamukhas — the country of, watered by Nalinī. 
Br. II. 18. 60.

श्वर
Śvara — a son of Dadhīci. 
Vā. 21. 42.

श्वलभ
Śvalabha — a Dānava. 
Br. III. 6. 12.

श्वशृप
Śvaśṛpa — a nephew of Hiraṇyakaśipu. 
M. 6. 27.

